lookupField

public static FieldDecl lookupField(Type t,
                                    Identifier id,
                                    TypeSig caller)
                             throws LookupException
This routine replaces javafe.tc.Types.lookupField. Unlike that routine, it knows about ghost fields and spec_public. This routine assumes we are in an annotation so ghost fields are visible and spec_public is equivalent to public.
